  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This technique uses the entire body as a spring, by amassing power through taking a posture where the back of the body falls down. With this powerful taijutsu, the user kicks just above the head. Because the power of the kick from the ground is instantly converted into a blow, the enemy hit with this attack will be launched high into the sky.</p><p>Make a melee Taijutsu attack, on a hit the target takes 4d10 bludgeoning damage, and is launched into the air 15 feet.</p><p>If this jutsu is cast as a <em><strong>Finisher</strong></em>, you instead deal your unarmed damage + 5d10 bludgeoning and knock the creature 30 feet into the air.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, the damage by 1d10, and the knockback by 10 feet.</p>",
